 and it is logical that the cool air will be denser than the warm air. 

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:38.400
 Because of the hot air, these particles have much higher kinetic energy 

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:41.580
 and they shall strike one another, and shall push one another 

00:02:41.580 --> 00:02:46.540
 far farther and far away from each other, 

00:02:46.540 --> 00:02:50.234
 due to this high average kinetic energy. 

